title: Google Accused of Abusing Monopoly Power
itunes:title: Google Accused of Abusing Monopoly Power
description:
Bloomberg Intelligence Senior Litigation Analyst Jennifer Rie and Michael Moe, Co-Founder of GSV Asset Management, discuss Google being accused of abusing monopoly power in a landmark U.S. case.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Paul Sweeney. Producer: Doni Holloway.
